OL,3,CFamily of pensioner tricked by con-men
OL,4,Csay his health has been devastated
OL,6,FWatch Sam Blackledge's report
OL,8,FThe family of a pensioner who was
OL,9,Ftricked into buying a gold bracelet
OL,10,Fworth thousands by two con-men have
OL,11,Fsaid the incident has had a
OL,12,Fdevastating effect on his dementia.
OL,14,FThe 88-year-old, from Falmouth, was
OL,15,Ftaken from his home by the rogue
OL,16,Ftraders to several bank branches in an
OL,17,Fattempt to force him to give them an
OL,18,Fup front payment for supposed roof
OL,19,Frepairs.
