OL,3,CFamily of pensioner tricked by con-men
OL,4,Csay his health has been devastated
OL,6,FAfter every bank refused to hand over
OL,7,Fany cash, Tommy Aaron Chislett and
OL,8,FShane Lee took the pensioner to a
OL,9,Fjewellery shop and tricked him into
OL,10,Fusing his bank card to pay for the
OL,11,F#3.5k bracelet.
OL,13,FThe man has not been named at his
OL,14,Ffamily's request.
OL,16,FDescribing the moment they knew
OL,17,Fsomething was wrong, the victim's son-
OL,18,Fin-law Phil Scala said: "It was a
OL,19,Fphone call from his bank - he was
OL,20,Ftrying to draw out a large amount for
OL,21,Fbuilding work.
