OL,3,CFamily of pensioner tricked by con-men
OL,4,Csay his health has been devastated
OL,6,F"When we got to his house, he wasn't
OL,7,Fthere - he'd left half eaten breakfast.
OL,9,F"So we went to the bank, and he wasn't
OL,10,Fthere either."
OL,12,FThe man's daughter, Stephanie Scala,
OL,13,Fsaid the incident has had a long term
OL,14,Feffect on her father.
OL,16,FShe said: "He was very independent,
OL,17,Ftaking care of himself but that whole
OL,18,Fepisode threw his confidence.
