OL,3,CFamily of pensioner tricked by con-men
OL,4,Csay his health has been devastated
OL,6,F"He was depressed after that, missing
OL,7,Fmeals and his medication. He's now in
OL,8,Fa care home because he couldn't live
OL,9,Fon his own."
OL,11,FTommy Chislett and Shane Lee were both
OL,12,Fjailed for two years at Truro Crown
OL,13,FCourt, after pleading guilty to
OL,14,Fattempted theft and fraud.
